entIdFromClientName` function seems perfect, and I can now confidently translate client names from the frontend to their corresponding IDs for API requests. This eliminates the assumptions I was making about equivalent naming. Now I am planning on replicating the same methodology to handle project identifiers, and figure out the `PROJECTS` available inside `/app/admin/documents/page.tsx`.\n\n\n"}}
